description: Annie’s Cheddar Gluten Free Mac and Cheese offers all the creamy yumminess of a kids food favorite for a part of family dinner everybunny will love. Made with rice pasta and real cheese, Annie's cheddar macaroni and cheese is a gluten-free adult and kids dinner option with zero compromises on taste. Annie's macaroni and cheese contains no artificial flavors or synthetic colors so you can feel good about serving and enjoying a great-tasting serving of gluten free pasta and cheese. This boxed pasta is perfect for lunchtime, dinnertime or anytime you're in the mood for something downright delicious. Annie's gluten free mac and cheese is ready in just ten minutes, helping you spend less time in the kitchen. Serve Annie's mac and cheese as a side dish or use it to prepare zucchini mac n cheese. This six-ounce box of Annie's mac and cheese is easy to store in the pantry and contains about two-and-a-half servings for a quick kids mac and cheese dinner option. Annie’s is devoted to spreading goodness through kindness to the planet and creating tasty foods for everybunny.
Annie’s Homegrown gluten-free rice pasta and cheddar mac and cheese

--ake delicious and yummy macaroni and cheese in a matter of minutes. It is very easy to prepare this scrumptious dish--just cook the pasta, squeeze in the creamy sauce, add butter for richer flavor, and serve--a dish your whole family will savor. This totally natural gluten-free offering is tailored for those who follow wheat-free or gluten-free diets, but it is so delicious that everyone will enjoy them! This product consists of no artificial colors, flavors, or preservatives, is processed without GMOs, and is free of trans fat and cholesterol. It is a good source of protein, calcium, and vitamin B6. This is sold in a pack of twelve 6-ounce boxes.

Annie’s Homegrown was co-founded in 1989 by Annie Withey, an organic farmer, wife, and mother of two.  Annie started with the intention of making all-natural macaroni and cheese. However, the company gained a lot of popularity and Annie’s currently does a lot more than that.

Annie’s Homegrown brings you a wide range of comfort foods such as macaroni and cheese, snacks, and cereal--all made with straight-from-nature, simple, and organic ingredients with no icky additives or pesky preservatives. All their products taste great--delight yourself with their delicious products now!

The company is driven by a team of folks who are passionate about three things--food, people, and the planet.  People at Annie’s Homegrown always strive for the motto: “Eat Responsibly. Act Responsibly”.
